{"id":150485,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/叙利亚再次发生暴力冲突26人死亡/","date":"2011-05-07T10:00:22Z","modified":"2011-05-07T10:00:22Z","title":"叙利亚再次发生暴力冲突26人死亡","content":"<div>\n<p><strong><span><br /></span></strong><span>大马士革</span></p>\n<p><span>周五弥撒结束后，叙利亚反对党的支持者和安全部队再次发生流血冲突，至少有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>名示威者丧生。据人权活动人士的报告，其中大多数人是在霍姆斯市（</span><span lang=\"DE\">Homs</span><span>）被打死。在首都大马士革，</span> <span>秘密警察逮捕了反对派领导人里亚德·赛义夫（</span><span lang=\"DE\">Riad Seif</span><span>）和著名神职人员阿尔·哈迪布（</span><span lang=\"DE\">Muas al-Chatib</span><span>）。成千上万的叙利亚人不顾政府的镇压威胁再次走上街头，要求民主变革和总统阿萨德下台。</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>个欧盟成员国已经决定对叙利亚政府对反对派的暴力镇压进行制裁。这些措施包括对叙利亚实行武器禁运，禁止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>名政府成员入境欧盟并冻结他们在欧盟的资产。关于对叙利亚总统阿萨德本人采取制裁措施的讨论将于下周一进行。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15057602%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%8126%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input n